#Task 37: Find K Largest Elements
# Get user input
nums = list(map(int, input("Enter numbers separated by spaces: ").split()))
k = int(input("Enter the value of k: "))

# Sort the list in descending order and take the first k elements
largest_k = sorted(nums, reverse=True)[:k]

print("K largest elements:", largest_k)

Enter numbers separated by spaces:  10 5 8 20 15 3
Enter the value of k:  3
K largest elements: [20, 15, 10]
